  The API endpoint has no access to the current epic, story, phase, failure_report, or retry counts. Every API-logged intervention entry will have empty/generic fields, producing the exact "vague summaries" AC #2 prohibits.

### Finding 3: CLI rebuild intervention passes empty epic/story
- **Severity:** HIGH
